    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Keyhole-style saws with a short blade that is supported in a pistol-style grip; frequently having interchangeable blades for different purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
